 ranks to become a manager.","markupType":"plain_text","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Strategy shift","markupType":"plain_text","type":"crosshead"},{"text":"&quot;At first, it felt strange to have staff who were older than me, or to have a boss who was younger than me, but I like how CyberAgent rewards its workers based on our performance, not our age,&quot; said Mr Oku.","markupType":"plain_text","type":"paragraph"},{"id":"88888724","subType":"body","href":"http://c.files.bbci.co.uk/A724/production/_88888724_cyberagent8.jpg","path":"/cpsprodpb/A724/production/_88888724_cyberagent8.jpg","height":351,"width":624,"altText":"Tetsuhito Soyama chatting with a manager at CyberAgent","caption":"CyberAgent's top managers had previously worked at traditional Japanese companies where they felt the reward system was unfair","copyrightHolder":"BBC","positionHint":"full-width","type":"image"},{"text":"It was their company policy from day one, said Tetsuhito Soyama, executive manager of human resources at CyberAgent. &quot;Many of our executives - including our founder - have worked at traditional Japanese companies before, which had the seniority wage system. But it felt odd because not everyone of the same age has the same ability.&quot; ","markupType":"plain_text","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"&quot;Our model means more competition and it is natural for older staff to feel jealous or awkward to see their younger colleagues being promoted first, but because it has been our corporate policy from the start, I think it was easier for us compared with older companies,&quot; he added.","markupType":"plain_text","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Failed attempts","markupType":"plain_text","type":"crosshead"},{"id":"88888720","subType":"body","href":"http://c.files.bbci.co.uk/0AE4/production/_88888720_cyberagent1.jpg","path":"/cpsprodpb/0AE4/production/_88888720_cyberagent1.jpg","height":549,"width":976,"altText":"Japanese office workers crossing the road","caption":"Japanese companies traditi